      <title>伯克希尔在审判前夕就飞行员旅行销售达成和解索赔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/berkshire-settles-claims-over-pilot-travel-sale-on-eve-of-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沃伦·巴菲特旗下的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司通过和解指控，改变了对交易最后部分进行估值的会计方法，从而违反了收购卡车停靠站连锁 Pilot Travel Centers 的条款，从而避免了审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-08/berkshire-settles-claims-over-pilot-travel-sale-on-eve-of-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 00:08:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
